data.description:
As you step into this beautiful home, you'll be greeted with a lovely entry way leading you to the expansive kitchen, featuring a large island overseeing the generously sized living room and a dining area large enough to accommodate any gathering you may host. The thoughtfully designed layout includes 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, and a 3-car garage. The primary suite boasts a luxurious soaking tub, a walk-in shower, double vanities, and an extensive walk-in closet with a built-in chest of drawers. **TWIN SILOS community includes wonderful amenities; beautiful large swimming pool with a clubhouse, private gym, pond, walking trails, basketball court, and a playground.

This home has 7 years remaining of the 10-year builder's warranty and is designed for energy efficiency, ensuring monthly savings on your utility bills.
